                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2235" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0347</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9119 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">突破重围，走向国际：海润集团国际营销之战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hairun: Mainland enterprise how to break the siege，to win the International market</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱新霞，黄存友</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东海润投资集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际营销；欧美市场；亚洲市场；丝绸行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">International Marketing; European and American Markets; Asia Markets; Silk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015年的两会和博鳌论坛上，“一带一路”无疑是万众瞩目的关键热词。3月28日，国家发改委、外交部、商务部发布了耗时两年的《推动共建丝绸之路经济带和海上丝绸之路的愿景与行动》。“一带一路”国家发展大战略愿景已出，行动在即，各界人士从中寻觅商机，思考新的发展方向。那么山东海润集团将怎样抓住“一带一路”的战略机遇，是郑总非常关心的问题。丝绸行业是中华民族文化瑰宝和历史文化的象征，丝绸素有纺织世家“皇后”之称，中国丝绸行业被列为中国典型出口导向型产业，其原料资源得天独厚的优势及产品颇强的国际竞争力均无与伦比。中国作为世界最大的生丝生产国和供应国，其中：蚕丝类产品出口多年居全国第一，真丝绸类产品出口位列全国第二。然而，金融危机和激烈的市场竞争对国际丝绸市场带来了巨大的冲击，市场形势的变化要求海润集团重新对国际市场营销战略进行定位和研究，如何打破以“市场占有率”为主导的传统营销模式，转向以“全面营销”为主导的国际营销模式？
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Chinese silk industry is the cultural treasures and a symbol of history and culture, silk textile family known as &quot;Queen,&quot; said the owner of the unique status symbol, reflecting the elegant taste of the wearer, the Chinese silk industry was classified as typical of China&#39;s export-oriented industries, its raw material resources rather unique advantage and a strong product competitiveness are unparalleled. China, the world&#39;s largest producer and supplier of raw silk, raw silk production accounts for more than 70% of world production, world exports of raw silk exports accounted for more than 90%, gray silk fabric export share of world exports of 60%.Hairun Group focuses on silk exports, export revenue accounted for 90% of total revenues, of which: exports of silk products for many years in the nation, silk products exports ranked second. However, the financial crisis on the international silk market has brought a huge impact on the market situation changes require Hairun Group to re-locate the international marketing strategy and research. However ,for Hairun ,how to break the traditional &quot;market share&quot;-oriented marketing modell, to establish a new &quot;comprehensive marketing&quot; oriented marketing model.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-12</td>
